nodes.text: Bogey 5632 was a clone trooper and member of Bogey Squad during the Great Jedi Purge on Kashyyyk.

Under Clone Commander Faie, 5632 and his squad hunted down Jedi Master Quinlan Vos after he survived the initial Order 66 attack. While approaching the injured Jedi Master alongside Bogey 4409, 5632 was eaten by an anakkona under the control of former General Vos.
